      • runService

        public java.util.List<java.lang.Object> runService(spark.Request req,
                                                   spark.Response res,
                                                   java.util.List<? extends Persistent> artifacts)
        Method to run the service. First, it calls prepareService and then exeService. Not to be override.
        Parameters:
        req - Java Spark Request. On request, request sent by user. Otherwise, request from basic services.
        res - Java Spark Response. On request, response sent by user. Otherwise, response from basic services.
        artifacts - List of artifacts. If called on request, is empty. If called after Upload, Download, Update, Delete, Read, has the object treated. If called after ReadAll or Search, has the objects found.
        Returns:
        output list from exeService.
